ActCanadian Energy Regulator Act
SubjectRegulations Amending Certain Regulations Made Under the National Energy Board Act (Miscellaneous Program)
PrecisRegulations amending CERTAIN REGULATIONS MADE UNDER THE NATIONAL ENERGY BOARD ACT (MISCELLANEOUS PROGRAM) in order to make amendments to certain names and terms in the Regulations for alignment with the Canadian Energy Regulator Act and to address the Standing Joint Committee for the Scrutiny of Regulations' queries on the 2013 National Energy Board Onshore Pipeline Regulations amendments.
